      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ jupyter kernelspec list&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Available kernels:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  julia-1.1    /home/matsueushi/.local/share/jupyter/kernels/julia-1.1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  python3      /home/matsueushi/.local/share/jupyter/kernels/python3&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;How do I add python3 kernel to jupyter (IPython)&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/28831854/how-do-i-add-python3-kernel-to-jupyter-ipython/44072803#44072803&#34;&gt;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/28831854/how-do-i-add-python3-kernel-to-jupyter-ipython/44072803#44072803&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
